Postgres Sequence Support
=========================

Very basic support for manipulating PostgreSQL sequences from ActiveRecord.

Examples
========

User.next_id              # => 1
User.current_id           # => 1

ActiveRecord::Base.connection.set_sequence('users_id_seq', 1000)
ActiveRecord::Base.connection.next_in_sequence('users_id_seq')
                          # => 1001


Homepage: http://github.com/jqr/postgres_sequence_support/tree/master  
